<h2>FAQ</h2>
<p><strong>Do I need to know how to code?</strong></p>
<p>No. Vibe coding requires clear description, not coding knowledge. You describe what you want. The AI writes the code.</p>
<p><strong>How long does it take to build a tool?</strong></p>
<p>Simple tools: 30-60 minutes. Medium tools: 1-3 hours. Complex tools: 3-8 hours. Most SEO tools are simple.</p>
<p><strong>What if the generated code has errors?</strong></p>
<p>Describe the error to the AI. It will fix it. Iteration is part of the process.</p>
<p><strong>Can I modify the code manually?</strong></p>
<p>Yes. If you understand code, you can edit directly. If not, describe changes to the AI.</p>
<p><strong>Are vibe-coded tools secure?</strong></p>
<p>Basic tools are secure. Do not build tools that handle sensitive data. Do not store user inputs. Use client-side processing when possible.</p>
<p><strong>How much do vibe coding tools cost?</strong></p>
